  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed dormer window would, being end of terrace, be clearly visible and would disrupt the otherwise unbroken roofline from 78-86 Treaty Street. The insertion of the dormer window would therefore have a harmful impact on the character and appearance of the surrounding streetscene and the host building. The proposal would be contrary to policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy 2011, policies D4 and D11 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002, and the Islington Urban Design Guidelines 2006."
